/encoder_decoder/v1_curriculum/data/**/index_removal_*.jsonl
/encoder_decoder/v1_curriculum/data/**/index_removal_*.md

# --- Allow selected v1_curriculum final checkpoint, inference logs and results ---
!encoder_decoder/v1_curriculum/checkpoints/
!encoder_decoder/v1_curriculum/checkpoints/README.md
!encoder_decoder/v1_curriculum/checkpoints/checkpoint_best.part*.pt
